;Courier New&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Comic Sans MS&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Given Module is &lt;i style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;less&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/i&gt; stable, and more prone to breakage due to changes in other modules.&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
